latestIgtvVideos.title: You are more than enough 💜
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Repost @kurve.official 

You are more than enough - Deby Lynn

People always judge us based on our appearance. They keep saying we are not enough. It affects me and makes me feel insecure

 Now I realize that, we don't need to care about what other people think about us. 
Thinking about ourselves is more important. When we feel good, we look good.

This is what #selflove is to me.
Don’t change who you are to please others
#womenempowerment #selflovekurve #kurvies

latestIgtvVideos.title: To endless to the ocean, to timeless to the tides.
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
It touches the deepest part of our souls to see this. Exquisitely beautiful memories and perfectly composed by @atipattra.co
We‘ve never imagined when we had to do this shoot without an amazing team to begin with and spent our 4 crazy days together 😂
They made us be ourselves, @leencarleen @alexanderalv , your beautiful souls captures our hearts ❤️
Even on the wedding day, we witnessed this all over again, we were still cried of joy. And we just couldn’t help to pour you guys with so much gratefulness and big bear hugs ❤️
.
